reviewText: Very funny, entertaining and possibly even 'educational' for aspiring players and pick up artists out there. Along with VH1's 'The Pick Up Artist', this is pretty much the only show featuring guys 'in field' attempting to pick up women in bars and clubs. Players, guys with game, guys with no game whatsoever, PUA's, Alpha males and Naturals, it sure beats watching soap operas!
This is a must have for all Keys To The Vip fans. Hopefully The DVD's are uncensored and have extra's. I have yet to receive the DVD's to write a proper review this is just based on I've seen on TV.
If you're a fan of the show and are wondering wether to buy this or the other seasons i say get em i put this on my ps3 and my hdtv and the sound and video is awesome definitely recommended.
